285
00:51:32,377 --> 00:51:41,454
Septembris; tamen errorem in hanc irrepsisse, nec ad primum, sed ad secundum Stiliconis consulatum, qui in laudatum annum 405 incidit, Acta illa esse referenda contendit.

286
00:51:41,454 --> 00:51:55,977
